metadata.name: POP CULTURE KIDS #1
metadata.description: PopCultureKids Epical Elon is 1 of 20 Series 1 characters consisting of 40 NFT cards with various rarity. This character is a parody of the famed billionaire Elon Musk. Elon is viewed by many as EPIC for his being CEO of Tesla, Space X and Starlink. Musk is also a huge supporter of cryptocurrency and is known as the DOGEfather.
